'''''Sprinter''''' was an [[CR92a Assassin-class corvette|''Assassin''-class corvette]] located at an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] scrap yard at [[Tolig IV]]. Its cargo were [[Speeder bike/Legends|speeder bikes]]. It was present there when [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace]] and [[Emon Azzameen]] went there to investigate the various containers to search for the Data Core, and when the raid took place.

